						<summary>

						<p>At the entrance (left side) to the central shrine of Nīlakaṇṭhēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Siṅghaṇa, 1223 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated the 13th regnal year of the king, Svabhānu, Āshāḍha śu. 5, Monday, corresponding to 1223 A.D., June 5.</p>						

						<p>It refers to a meritorious act whose nature is not specified, by Hirubāyi, wife of <hi rend="italic">Sarvādhikāri</hi> Purushōttama-nāyaka.</p>						

